|2 |  ├─TABLE RANGE SCAN      |bmsql_stock     |1       |3           |
|3 |  └─SORT                  |                |1       |21          |
|4 |    └─SUBPLAN SCAN        |VIEW1           |1       |21          |
|5 |      └─NESTED-LOOP JOIN  |                |1       |21          |
|6 |        ├─TABLE GET       |bmsql_district  |1       |5           |
|7 |        └─TABLE RANGE SCAN|bmsql_order_line|1       |16          |
======================================================================
